{"word":"G514 - ἄξιος - áxios - ax'-ee-os - Due reward","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄξιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áxios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ax'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Due reward</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஏற்ற, பாத்திரமான, தக்க, தகுதியான,"},{"paragraph":"ஒப்பிடத்தக்க - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"weighing, having weight, befitting, congruous, corresponding,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; <i>deserving</i>, <i>comparable</i> or <i>suitable</i> (as if <i>drawing</i> praise): - due reward, meet, [un-] worthy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2661/2661\">G2661</a>, <a href=\"#/G370/370\">G370</a>, <a href=\"#/G514/514\">G514</a>, <a href=\"#/G515/515\">G515</a>"}]}